description:
The Tree That Saved Christmas




Struggling writer Annie Logan is devastated to learn that she won't be able to go home to the family tree farm in time for Christmas due to the demands of her high-powered boss. But when the tree farm is threatened with closure, all in the name of a new golf course, Annie bids her life in New York and rushes home to save the place she has always called home.




Original Air Date: 30-Nov-2014
